    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>This is a demo version!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Push, combine, and deliver pastries with the help of your hats in Hat Helpers, a cozy 3D grid-based puzzle game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258340/extras/38dfccabe53935ced967e9d144b178b0.poster.avif?t=1738240323\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258340/extras/38dfccabe53935ced967e9d144b178b0.webm?t=1738240323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258340/extras/38dfccabe53935ced967e9d144b178b0.mp4?t=1738240323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzles centered around one simple mechanic pushed to its limits</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every puzzle is unique and teaches you something new</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interesting solutions with a focus on &quot;Aha!&quot; moments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Made one wrong move? Don't worry! Just press Z to undo any mistake</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No distractions, just fun puzzles! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258340/extras/12d5b5aa02276dedd5c7db24cca0b6c2.poster.avif?t=1738240323\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258340/extras/12d5b5aa02276dedd5c7db24cca0b6c2.webm?t=1738240323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akama